{"inkVersion":21,"root":[[{"->":"INTRO"},["done",{"#n":"g-0"}],null],"done",{"INTRO":["^2640__PAUSE__","\n","#","^slow:38","/#","^You wake.","\n","^__NL__","\n","^1700__PAUSE__","\n","^The stone beneath you is cold, not unlike ice. It consumes what little light is in the room. Painful chains surround you and bite into your limbs, like ravenous snakes.","\n","^1275__PAUSE__","\n","^765__PAUSE__","\n","^__NL__","\n","#","^slow:32","/#","^<sfx=sfx-shake-weak><i>What... where... am I?</i></sfx=sfx-shake-weak> 26<~>you think.</~>","\n","^__NL__","\n","^765__PAUSE__","\n","#","^slow:27","/#","^Your thoughts move like insects in glue; 23<~>they feel trapped, with no end in sight.</~> Trapped. Just like you.","\n","^1020__PAUSE__","\n","#","^slow:16","/#","^Three hooded figures surround you.","\n","^1275__PAUSE__","\n","^__NL__","\n","^__S:Judgement__","\n","#","^slow:25","/#","^\"It wakes.\"","\n","^680__PAUSE__","\n","^__NL__","\n","^__S:Truth__","\n","#","^slow:20","/#","^Another voice drifts from your left. 26<~>\"Does it know its name?\"</~>","\n","^425__PAUSE__","\n","#","^slow:18","/#","^A pair of blue eyes glint faintly, locked on you without blinking.","\n","^1190__PAUSE__","\n","^__NL__","\n","#","^slow:23","/#","^Your head hurts.","\n","^1105__PAUSE__","\n","^__NL__","\n","#","^slow:19","/#","^A scoff from your right — low, sharp, and dripping with disdain. Red eyes burn faintly in the dark.","\n","^__S:Mercy__","\n","^\"Why waste time, we—\"","\n","^__NL__","\n","^__S:Judgement__","\n","#","^slow:18","/#","^\"Peace.\"","\n","^The center figure’s tone cuts the air clean in half. The others fall silent instantly.","\n","#","^slow:19","/#","^The one in the middle fixes you with a stare so steady you shiver, 16<~>though not from the cold. </~>","\n","^300__PAUSE__","\n","^__S:Judgement__","\n","^\"Speak. Do you remember your name?\"","\n","^850__PAUSE__","\n","^__NL__","\n","#","^slow:26","/#","^You cannot resist. It binds to you, like an old scar reopening.","\n","ev",0.12,13.0,-1,0,{"x()":"animateBlur","exArgs":4},"pop","/ev","\n","#","^slow:28","/#","^Cold floods your vision. The floor tilts.","\n","^You try to cry, to shout, to scream... but your tongue has forgotten the shape of sound.","\n","^__NL__","\n","ev","str","^Ossaneth","/str",{"x()":"playerForceMask","exArgs":1},"pop","/ev","\n","#","^slow:24","/#","^A voice curls behind your thoughts — smooth, flat, and unbearably near.","\n","^__NL__","\n","^__S:Ossaneth__","\n","#","^slow:30","/#","^<sfx=sfx-shake>\"Call me Ossaneth, the Unblinking Eye.\"</sfx=sfx-shake>","\n","^__S:Ossaneth__","\n","#","^slow:25","/#","^<sfx=sfx-shake>\"I see what is, what was, and what shall be. And now you will too.\"</sfx=sfx-shake>","\n","^1700__PAUSE__","\n","ev",0.25,3.0,-1,0,{"x()":"animateBlur","exArgs":4},"pop","/ev","\n","^__S:Ossaneth__","\n","#","^slow:26","/#","^<sfx=sfx-shake-strong>\"Share in the Sight, friend.\"</sfx=sfx-shake-strong>","\n","^850__PAUSE__","\n","^__NL__","\n","#","^slow:32","/#","^You faint.","\n","ev",0.9,2.0,3.0,4.0,{"x()":"animateBlur","exArgs":4},"pop","/ev","\n","ev","str","^Player.Received.OssanethMask","/str",true,{"x()":"setFlag","exArgs":2},"pop","/ev","\n","ev","str","^Player.CurrentSceneNo","/str",1,{"x()":"setCounter","exArgs":2},"pop","/ev","\n","ev","str","^Player.TimesEncountered.Witnesses","/str",1,{"x()":"setCounter","exArgs":2},"pop","/ev","\n","^3200__PAUSE__","\n","^2000__PAUSE__","\n","^__NL__","\n","^__NL__","\n","^__NL__","\n","#","^slow:25","/#","^You wake once more.","\n","^__NL__","\n","^__END__","\n","end",null],"setFlag":[{"temp=":"value"},{"temp=":"key"},"ev","void","/ev","~ret",null],"playerForceMask":[{"temp=":"maskName"},"ev","void","/ev","~ret",null],"setCounter":[{"temp=":"value"},{"temp=":"key"},"ev","void","/ev","~ret",null],"getLabel":[{"temp=":"key"},"ev","void","/ev","~ret",null],"setLabel":[{"temp=":"value"},{"temp=":"key"},"ev","void","/ev","~ret",null],"setSilentPath":[{"temp=":"silentMs"},{"temp=":"silentPath"},"ev","void","/ev","~ret",null],"animateBlur":[{"temp=":"waitSecs"},{"temp=":"fadeBackDurationSecs"},{"temp=":"durationSecs"},{"temp=":"targetOpacity"},"ev","void","/ev","~ret",null],"global decl":["ev",0,{"VAR=":"questionsAsked"},"/ev","end",null]}],"listDefs":{}}